                    <td class="forumAlternate" >I'll have a go at answering some of your questions.  AA is Alternate Advancement.  It allows you to put all or a portion of your experience into these points instead of just leveling after you reach level 50.  The hoards you see in Butcherblock are at one of the wayfarer camps that were added with the Lost Dungeon's of Norrath expansion.  Augs are augmentation gems that drop in the LDoN adventures.  They can be applied to weapons or armor to add stats or resists.  It's a way to improve some of ...</td>
