                  <tr>
                    <td class="forumAlternate" >Just to give you a hard number example and hopefully make it clearer.  Fufil's Curtailing Chant (lvl 30) does a minimum of 11 points damage and 9 point Magic Resist debuff if you are just warbling the chant.  Put a store-bought drum (1.8 mod) in your hand for accompaniment, and you do 1.8 times 11 or 19 points, and 16 points of MR.  TDoK gives you 30 damage and 25 MR.  The level of the Bard does not matter, which is why the higher mod instruments are so sought after.</td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
