                    <td>Simply turn on auto-attack and have at.  Twist your songs, and the game will work a blow in when it needs to without interupting the song.  Your hand-to-hand skill will rise until you:  A.  get dual wield at 17 and get primary hand instruments; or B.  learn to rapidly switch instruments and weapons.  

All of our songs pretty much have the same duration.  3 seconds to cast and 18 seconds effect.  In theory, we should be able to keep 6 songs going but in practice, 3 is about all we can ...</td>
