                    <td class="forumAlternate" >One reason that it is not mentioned much, is that it is NO DROP, Vah Shir only.  If you are a Kitty bard like me, it is the bee's knees 'till I get a few more level's on me.  If you're not, it just makes you jealous. (I have also gotten quite a few double takes with my lute in one hand and a sword in the other.)   :D 

